00:22:00.577 --> 00:22:02.360
ikh hob gegat a mentsh

00:22:02.872 --> 00:22:04.554
vos hot gemakht sakharin.

00:22:05.555 --> 00:22:07.423
sakharin. a mashin hot er...

00:22:07.547 --> 00:22:09.516
er iz geven a mekhanik, a shloser,

00:22:09.639 --> 00:22:11.928
un hot gemakht a mashindl vos s'iz aroysgegangen

00:22:12.052 --> 00:22:13.953
hundert un tsvey tabletn

00:22:14.246 --> 00:22:15.337
sakharin.

00:22:16.001 --> 00:22:17.717
bin ikh arayngeforn,

00:22:18.195 --> 00:22:20.518
un er hot gezogt ikh zol arbetn mit im, dos ton.

00:22:21.283 --> 00:22:23.100
se geyt arayn aza puder,

00:22:23.223 --> 00:22:26.005
in di shif-redl, un me rukt es arayn,

00:22:26.005 --> 00:22:30.440
filt zikh op hundert un tsvey lefelekh, azoy, un se geyt aroys tabletn.

00:22:31.593 --> 00:22:32.482
un shoyn.

00:22:32.606 --> 00:22:34.223
a klal, ober vu vet men arbetn?

00:22:34.223 --> 00:22:35.418
hot men genumen

00:22:35.795 --> 00:22:37.004
azoy vi yetst

00:22:37.196 --> 00:22:38.912
a a, iz er geven

00:22:39.238 --> 00:22:41.589
a groyser, tsu a MAYOR, tsu vos,

00:22:41.634 --> 00:22:44.548
hot er gezogt, "ikh vel zayn, ikh vel enk opgebn a GARAGE

00:22:44.857 --> 00:22:46.069
oyf di UNK,

00:22:46.072 --> 00:22:47.636
vu di rusn zenen,

00:22:47.760 --> 00:22:49.762
un ets kont, dort kont ets arbetn.

00:22:49.920 --> 00:22:51.264
dort kont ets arbetn."

00:22:52.265 --> 00:22:53.593
me iz arayngeganen,

00:22:54.324 --> 00:22:56.411
un ikh bin dort arayngeganen arbetn,

00:22:57.058 --> 00:22:58.841
hobn mir gemakht eyn tog

00:22:59.808 --> 00:23:00.950
epes

00:23:02.762 --> 00:23:06.767
fuftsn kilo, tsi tsvelef kilo, ikh veys nisht vifl s'iz gevezn, UNK,

00:23:06.767 --> 00:23:10.333
di sakharin, di PILLelekh, me hot nisht gehat keyn PILLelekh, not men gemuzt koyfn di PILLelekh.

00:23:10.760 --> 00:23:14.787
nu, ikh hob gezen az in der fri, me geyt es farkoyfn, kumt men tsu tsu di drotn,

00:23:15.047 --> 00:23:19.429
tsum lager, me khapt es fun di hent, me shtupt arayn gelt, me lozt undz geyn vifl me hot nor.

00:23:20.396 --> 00:23:24.525
nu, hot men shoyn gezen az s'iz a, s'iz an ar-, s'iz a biznes, an artikl.

00:23:24.800 --> 00:23:27.866
un di DEUTSCHen hobn geshribn keseyder in di PAPER,

00:23:27.973 --> 00:23:31.325
az zey zukhn di shpekulantn, oyf undz, vos men makht nokh.

00:23:31.449 --> 00:23:34.532
undzer zakharin hot men gekent arayntun fir shtik in a gloz arayn.

00:23:34.773 --> 00:23:36.303
un s'iz nisht geven zis.

00:23:36.377 --> 00:23:38.953
un zeyer's hot men arayngeleygt eyns un s'iz geven zis.

00:23:39.701 --> 00:23:40.404
nu.

00:23:40.680 --> 00:23:44.972
vos hot ikh gezolt tun? hot men dos gemakht mit di, a a por vokhn, biz me hot

00:23:44.983 --> 00:23:46.429
untergekhapt undz.

00:23:46.788 --> 00:23:48.791
di DEUTSCHen hobn undz untergekhapt,

00:23:49.083 --> 00:23:51.153
un me hot undz arayngenumen ale,

00:23:51.210 --> 00:23:52.498
in a tfise arayn,

00:23:52.543 --> 00:23:55.558
un me hot undz gefregt ve-, tsu vemen balangt di mashin?

00:23:56.559 --> 00:24:00.738
yeder hot zikh, hot gezogt, "nisht tsu mir," "nisht tsu mir," "nisht tsu..." me hot dokh moyre gehat dem dos.

00:24:00.795 --> 00:24:03.557
ober me hot undz gegebn tsu esn dort gut, un ales,

00:24:04.001 --> 00:24:07.981
nu, un biz me, me iz gezesn efsher tsvey tog, ⟨gelt⟩ hot men gehat UNK droysn,

00:24:08.000 --> 00:24:09.648
UNK, bakante.

00:24:09.992 --> 00:24:14.256
arayngeshikt a LAWYER, mit mayses, un der UNK iz gekumen, me hot undz aroysgenumen

00:24:14.717 --> 00:24:15.910
fun tfise,

00:24:16.134 --> 00:24:18.283
tsurikgeforn, avek UNK UNK.

00:24:18.294 --> 00:24:19.486
ven iz dos geven?

00:24:20.133 --> 00:24:24.104
dos iz gevezn, ven ikh bin shoyn gevezn in in Berlin.

00:24:24.104 --> 00:24:28.467
nokh bafrayung, nokhn bafrayung, s'iz shoyn geven nayntsn zibn un fertsik, akht un fertsik.

00:24:28.467 --> 00:24:29.898
biz nayn un fertsik.

00:24:31.693 --> 00:24:34.472
un nayn un fertsik bin ikh geforn nokh ISRAEL avek.

00:24:35.979 --> 00:24:39.315
ikh hob gegat an, a khaver, hot er gehat a BOY,

00:24:39.489 --> 00:24:41.267
iz er alt geven elef yor.

00:24:41.278 --> 00:24:42.369
oysbahaltn.

00:24:43.674 --> 00:24:47.786
hot men im gezogt az, az me geyt forn nokh ISRAEL, az er iz nisht mal geven,

00:24:47.859 --> 00:24:49.878
vet men nisht araynlozn nokh ISRAEL.

00:24:50.964 --> 00:24:52.396
iz geven a dokter,

00:24:52.396 --> 00:24:56.325
fun Tshenstekhov, hot er geheysn DOBZHINSKI, dokter DOBZHINSKI, a groyser

00:24:56.499 --> 00:24:57.540
SURGEON.

00:24:58.001 --> 00:25:07.462
hob ikh UNK, ikh hob azoy vi yetst gehaltn di fis, un me hot im aropgevizn, dem BOY, un me iz geforn nokh ISRAEL arayn, ikh mit im, mit di froy, arayn, mitn kind.

00:25:08.582 --> 00:25:10.393
er iz arayngekumen nokh ISRAEL,

00:25:10.393 --> 00:25:11.870
hot men undz gegebn

00:25:11.906 --> 00:25:14.021
azane palatkes, tsu voynen,

00:25:14.066 --> 00:25:15.107
oyfn feld,

00:25:15.365 --> 00:25:17.573
tsutsumakhn oyf oyf SNAPS,

00:25:17.573 --> 00:25:19.578
dort ze'mir ge-, a vint iz gevezn!

00:25:19.989 --> 00:25:22.905
un der BOY, der BOY hot zikh onge-, dos kind hot zikh ongerufn,

00:25:22.908 --> 00:25:25.906
"zen dos, di shtub," zogt zi, "men darf tsumakhn

00:25:26.030 --> 00:25:28.989
oyf oyf SNAPS dem dem di...

00:25:28.989 --> 00:25:30.750
tirn, mit di fentster,

00:25:30.975 --> 00:25:34.648
vos hostu do UNK, UNK un aza vint, un kalt..."

00:25:35.717 --> 00:25:39.880
shoyn. m'iz dort gevezn a tsvey tog, un me hot undz arayngeshikt in a

00:25:40.340 --> 00:25:42.123
in a PLACE vos iz shoyn

00:25:42.298 --> 00:25:46.241
azoy vi mentshn, oyf betlekh lign oysgeleygt, efsher a

00:25:46.382 --> 00:25:49.616
a hundert mentshn yede barak, azoy bazunder oysgeleygt.

00:25:50.229 --> 00:25:51.725
un m'iz dort geshtanen.

00:25:53.199 --> 00:25:54.071
biz

00:25:55.089 --> 00:25:59.994
me hot aroysgenumen dort fun

00:26:07.053 --> 00:26:08.510
hot er gebrengt dort a

00:26:08.510 --> 00:26:11.013
a rumener, hob ikh genumen a UNK, ikh hob im batsolt,

00:26:11.154 --> 00:26:12.482
tsvey hundert

00:26:12.740 --> 00:26:13.556
funt

00:26:13.584 --> 00:26:15.806
a monat far, tsu voynen dort.

00:26:16.925 --> 00:26:19.167
bin ikh gevoynt dort efsher zeks khadoshim.

00:26:19.167 --> 00:26:22.472
nokh di zeks khadoshim bin ikh tsurikgeforn, ikh hob ayngegebn far mayn froy

00:26:22.848 --> 00:26:24.727
oyf a vize, aroystsuforn,

00:26:24.755 --> 00:26:26.217
a nay- aroys,

00:26:26.325 --> 00:26:29.914
vayl yeder hot gevolt a nay-rayz vize, vayl me hot nisht gelozt aroysforn UNK.

00:26:30.392 --> 00:26:35.415
hobn zey ir, hot mikh der UNK gerufn, "far vos vilstu aroysforn?" zog ikh, "zest dokh, mayn vayb iz a kranke.

00:26:35.758 --> 00:26:37.136
zi kon nisht nemen

00:26:37.665 --> 00:26:40.106
dem di hits, zi kon nisht dos nisht nemen."

00:26:40.398 --> 00:26:43.902
hot er gezogt, "ikh vel dikh shikn arayn nokh Yerusholaim, dort iz

00:26:44.381 --> 00:26:45.388
iz kil."

00:26:46.237 --> 00:26:49.741
ober se hot nisht getoygt far Yerusholaim oykhet. hot er gezogt,

00:26:50.523 --> 00:26:52.542
"dos kon ikh dir tun, meyn nisht."

00:26:52.835 --> 00:26:53.499
nu.

00:26:53.544 --> 00:26:54.973
vos tut men vayter?

00:26:55.181 --> 00:26:56.475
bin ikh gegangen

00:26:57.763 --> 00:27:01.014
arop tsu di, tsu ISRAEL, dort tsu di shifn.

00:27:01.661 --> 00:27:02.719
un ikh hob gevolt

00:27:03.011 --> 00:27:04.122
aroysforn.

00:27:04.122 --> 00:27:07.916
hot mikh eyner gevolt aroyfnemen, a CAPTAIN, als an arbeter oyf di

00:27:07.989 --> 00:27:09.587
shif, mit mayn vayb,

00:27:09.845 --> 00:27:13.501
un me vet konen, azoy nor vet men konen forn, nokh ITALY.

00:27:14.807 --> 00:27:19.858
yedes mol ikh bin geganen, hot er gezogt ikh zol im gebn fuftsik funt, fuftsik funt, ikh hob im shoyn gehat gegebn

00:27:19.903 --> 00:27:22.800
efsher tsvey hundert fuftsik funt hot er aroysgetsoygn fun mir,

00:27:23.295 --> 00:27:26.445
un ey-, un s'iz gornisht gevezn, zogt er, tomer vel ikh hoykh redn,

00:27:26.585 --> 00:27:29.684
vel ikh shoyn in gantsn nisht aroysforn, shoyn, hob ikh moyre gekrign.

00:27:30.905 --> 00:27:32.165
UNK nisht geredt.

00:27:32.508 --> 00:27:34.443
nokh dem iz er geganen

00:27:35.900 --> 00:27:37.970
yo, bin ikh geganen nokh a mol,

00:27:38.027 --> 00:27:42.038
aroyf tsum Italyenisher konsul, in dort in in ISRAEL.

00:27:42.448 --> 00:27:44.957
hob ikh gegat a goldenem zeyger, an OMEGA,

00:27:45.468 --> 00:27:47.082
bin ikh aroyfgeganen tsun im,

00:27:47.156 --> 00:27:51.926
hob ikh arayngeleygt in zeyger in UNK, un ikh hob UNK oyfn tish, zog ikh, "horkht mikh oys,

00:27:52.303 --> 00:27:53.985
ikh vil aroysforn

00:27:54.159 --> 00:27:57.039
un UNK konstu mir gebn a vize, a nay-rayz vize,

00:27:57.112 --> 00:27:59.941
az ikh zol konen aroysforn mit mayn froy, mitn kind?"

00:28:00.352 --> 00:28:03.316
zogt er tsu mir, dos kon er nisht gebn, nor ikh muz,

00:28:03.575 --> 00:28:06.911
er kon mir eyn zakh makhn, ikh zol koyfn TICKETS oyf ahin un tsurik,

00:28:07.136 --> 00:28:09.054
ikh for oyf a lust-rayze.

00:28:09.549 --> 00:28:10.590
vet er mir,

00:28:11.203 --> 00:28:12.947
kon er mir gebn TICKETS.

00:28:12.947 --> 00:28:13.914
UNK

00:28:14.139 --> 00:28:16.108
vos a khilek? az s'iz a lust-rayze.

00:28:16.265 --> 00:28:17.103
shoyn.

00:28:17.548 --> 00:28:19.061
bin ikh arayngekumen

00:28:19.792 --> 00:28:20.816
tsun im,

00:28:20.889 --> 00:28:24.261
un er hot mir geheysn kumen fraytik, azoy vi yetst iz gevezn,

00:28:24.298 --> 00:28:25.777
er hot mir gegebn di TICKET,

00:28:26.070 --> 00:28:28.731
un ikh hob gemuzt batsoln far di TICKET ahin un tsurik,

00:28:29.057 --> 00:28:31.195
oyf a lust-rayze, ahin un tsurik.

00:28:31.588 --> 00:28:34.294
un ikh bin gekumen aheym, mayn vayb, ale, zey hobn

00:28:34.294 --> 00:28:36.661
nisht gevolt gleybn in di velt az ikh hob TICKETS.

00:28:36.752 --> 00:28:37.793
zog ikh, "kum."

00:28:38.321 --> 00:28:39.525
bin ikh gegangen

00:28:39.525 --> 00:28:40.866
aroyf oyf di shif,

00:28:40.866 --> 00:28:43.597
un gefort arayn nokh ISRAEL- nokh,

00:28:43.755 --> 00:28:44.998
tsurik arayn

00:28:45.189 --> 00:28:46.612
fun,

00:28:46.612 --> 00:28:48.457
ISRAEL arayn nokh DEUTCHLAND.

00:28:49.104 --> 00:28:52.203
ikh bin aroyfgegangen oyf di shif hot men genumen dos UNK fun kind,

00:28:52.597 --> 00:28:54.096
tsushroyft yedes,

00:28:54.096 --> 00:28:58.177
yedes redl aropgenumen, un gezukht, un gezukht, un gezukht

00:28:58.284 --> 00:29:00.438
nokh dem ikh bin aroyf oyf di shif hob ikh gezen

00:29:01.237 --> 00:29:06.885
UNK esn, un un epl, un frukhtn, a ale, s'iz an ander lebn.

00:29:07.413 --> 00:29:09.096
ikh bin aroyfgekumen,
